OL,3,CPolice operation in Co Armagh village
OL,4,Cas counter protests take place
OL,6,FA pro-Palestine march and counter-
OL,7,Fprotest have passed off without major
OL,8,Fincident in Co Down amid a heavy
OL,9,Fpolice presence.
OL,11,FPolice officers, armoured Land Rovers,
OL,12,Friot squad members and water cannons
OL,13,Fwere among resources in place ahead of
OL,14,Fthe events in the afternoon.
OL,16,FThe Great March for Gaza, organised by
OL,17,Fthe Ireland-Palestine Solidarity
OL,18,FCampaign (IPSC) in Lurgan, set off
OL,19,Ffrom the Co Armagh town towards Newry,
OL,20,Fto represent the 25-mile length of the
OL,21,FGaza Strip.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
