OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1780942271
OL,3,CPolice operation in Co Armagh village
OL,4,Cas counter protests take place
OL,6,FIt aims to raise money for Palestine
OL,7,FAid Ireland and Children Not Numbers.
OL,9,FThe procession travelled along the
OL,10,FNewry towpath for part of the way,
OL,11,Fpassing Scarva, where local residents
OL,12,Fhad raised objections.
OL,14,FThe Parades Commission granted
OL,15,Fpermission for the march, but placed a
OL,16,Fnumber of conditions on it, including
OL,17,Fthat no participant should enter
OL,18,FScarva.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
