OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1780942271
OL,3,CPolice operation in Co Armagh village
OL,4,Cas counter protests take place
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a group called Scarva
OL,7,FConcerned Residents had permission for
OL,8,Fa demonstration on Scarva Bridge, with
OL,9,Fconditions including refraining from
OL,10,F"provocative behaviour".
OL,12,FHundreds of protesters with Israel
OL,13,Fflags as well as Union flags turned
OL,14,Fout to oppose the march.
OL,16,FA line of police Land Rovers blocked
OL,17,Foff the bridge which connects the
OL,18,Ftowpath and the village.
