OL,3,CPolice operation in Co Armagh village
OL,4,Cas counter protests take place
OL,6,FAs the march passed along the towpath,
OL,7,Fprotesters on the other side of the
OL,8,Fcanal watched on.
OL,10,FIt came after a similar event last
OL,11,Fyear which saw what police termed as
OL,12,F"minor disorder" and four arrests, as
OL,13,Fwell as number of people cautioned.
